Beat canola oil with sugar. Whisk in egg and molasses. Add flour, ginger, cinnamon, baking powder, baking soda and salt. Stir until dough is moist. Using 1 teaspoon per cookie, shape dough into a ball. Roll in sugar. Bake on lightly oiled cookie sheets at 375 degrees F for 12-15 minutes. Let cool on cookie sheets or racks.